Folium 으로 지도 활용하기¶

스타벅스 이디야 카페 매장 전체 분포¶

  • Marker CircleMarker .
In [9]:
import folium

lat = df_cafe[''].mean()
long = df_cafe[''].mean()

m = folium.Map([lat, long], zoom_start=11, tiles='Stamentoner')

for i in df_cafe.index:
    sub_lat = df_cafe.loc[i, '']
    sub_long = df_cafe.loc[i, '']
    
    title = f"{df_cafe.loc[i, '']} - {df_cafe.loc[i, '']}"
    
    icon_color = 'blue'
    if df_cafe.loc[i, ''] == '':
        icon_color = 'green'
        
    folium.CircleMarker([sub_lat, sub_long], 
                    color=icon_color,
                    radius=3,
                    tooltip=title).add_to(m)
m

choropleth 를 위한 GeoJSON 파일로드¶

In [10]:
geo_path = 'data/seoul_municipalities_geo_simple.json'

import json
geo_json = json.load(open(geo_path, encoding="utf-8"))

스타벅스 매장 분포¶

In [11]:
df_star = df_cafe_vs[df_cafe_vs[''] == ''].copy()
In [12]:
m = folium.Map([lat, long], zoom_start=11, tiles='Stamentoner')

folium.Choropleth(
    geo_data=geo_json,
    name="choropleth",
    data=df_star,
    columns=["", ""],
    key_on="feature.properties.name",
    fill_color="YlGn",
    fill_opacity=0.7,
    line_opacity=0.2,
    legend_name=" ",
).add_to(m)

In [19]:
df_vs = df_vs.merge(df_gu_mean, how='inner', left_on='', right_on='')
In [20]:
m = folium.Map([lat, long], zoom_start=11, tiles='Stamentoner')

folium.Choropleth(
    geo_data=geo_json,
    name="choropleth",
    data=df_vs,
    columns=["", ""],
    key_on="feature.properties.name",
    fill_color="BuGn",
    fill_opacity=0.7,
    line_opacity=0.2,
    legend_name=" (   )",
).add_to(m)

for i in df_vs.index:
    sub_lat = df_vs.loc[i, '']
    sub_long = df_vs.loc[i, '']
    
    cafes = ['', '']
    for cafe in cafes:
        cafe_count = df_vs.loc[i, cafe]
        radius = np.sqrt(cafe_count) * 3
        
        gu = df_vs.loc[i, '']
        tooltip = f'{gu} {cafe} : {cafe_count}'
        
        color = 'green'
        if cafe == '':
            color = 'blue'
            sub_long+=0.01
            
        folium.CircleMarker([sub_lat, sub_long],
                            radius=radius,
                            fill=True,
                            tooltip=tooltip,
                            color = color).add_to(m)

m
